text.tspan: Notes
June 13, 2023: v2.6: Control lives and bug fixes.
March 27, 2023: v2.5: New key features added.
March 25, 2023: v2.4: Made worlds more interesting.
February 17, 2023: v2.3: New triggers added.
February 12, 2023: v2.2: New clicker game added.
February 11, 2023: v2.1: Gravity portals added.
February 3, 2023: v2.0: New hats made.
January 1, 2023: v1.9: Added spawn points. Fixed a lot of bugs.
December 31, 2022: v1.8: Added a loading screen, and added placeable blocks, lives, chests, and food!
December 30, 2022: v1.7: Made the updates in the game, removed common Q & A,
made a level pack list. Hopefully we get levels soon!
December 29, 2022: v1.6: Added level 10, Mysteries.
December 28, 2022: v1.5: Nerfed the game a bit because it was too hard.
December 27, 2022: v1.4: Added camera controls! Use these to hide secrets in your levels.
Also updates are added in the menu.
December 26, 2022: v1.3: Added lots of new features, including ship, wheel, and
booster mode, as well as size orbs.
December 25, 2022: v1.2: Added bird, as well as changing the flag textures.
December 18, 2022: v1.1: Random World Generation! Mine for orbs!
You can access this update by Menu, Level Editor. Click "O" to edit, then
"R" to reset the level. Answer
"Yes," then answer "0" to generate your own world! Press "Q" to save the level,
copy the code, then go to Menu, Play, Load. Paste the level code and mine!
December 9, 2022: v1.0: Full Version Release
October 9, 2022: v0.5: Beta version released as Multiplayer (Outdated)
September 16, 2022: v0.2: Updated to Alpha. (Unavailable)
August 8, 2022: v0.01: Pre-Alpha version released. (Unavailable)
